                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "The agent is trained for 1M steps on an infinite- horizon task with partial episodes lasting 200 steps. When the last step of a partial episode is encountered, a truncated signal is emitted and PEB is performed, recalling the agent that additional steps and rewards would actually be available thereafter [12]."
